{"comments":"Shadow style compounds — aesthetic shadow presets.\n\n## Design Philosophy\n\nThese compounds represent **stylistic choices** rather than semantic\nelevation. They define the aesthetic quality of a shadow:\n\n- **Soft**: Diffuse, gentle shadows (modern, minimal)\n- **Hard**: Crisp, defined shadows (bold, graphic)\n- **Layered**: Multiple shadows for depth (realistic, premium)\n- **Colored**: Tinted shadows matching element (playful, branded)\n- **Long**: Extended shadows (dramatic, low sun angle)\n\n## Relationship to SemanticElevation\n\nSemanticElevation defines WHAT level (flat, raised, floating, etc.)\nShadowStyle defines HOW that elevation looks visually.\n\nA modal dialog might be at Elevation4 (Modal level) but rendered with\neither ShadowSoft for a gentle appearance or ShadowHard for emphasis.\n\n## Usage\n\n```purescript\nimport Hydrogen.Schema.Elevation.ShadowStyle as SS\nimport Hydrogen.Schema.Color.RGB as RGB\n\n-- Get a soft shadow with intensity 2 (1-5 scale)\ncardShadow = SS.shadowSoft 2\n\n-- Get a colored shadow based on element color\ncoloredShadow = SS.shadowColored (RGB.rgb 59 130 246) 3\n\n-- Convert to CSS\ncss = SS.toLegacyCss cardShadow\n```\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[131,9],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Elevation/ShadowStyle.purs","start":[131,3]},"title":"None"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Elevation","ShadowStyle"],"Intensity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Elevation","Shadow"],"LayeredShadow"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[132,9],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Elevation/ShadowStyle.purs","start":[132,3]},"title":"Soft"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Elevation","ShadowStyle"],"Intensity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Elevation","Shadow"],"LayeredShadow"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[133,9],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Elevation/ShadowStyle.purs","start":[133,3]},"title":"Hard"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Elevation","ShadowStyle"],"Intensity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Elevation","Shadow"],"LayeredShadow"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[134,12],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Elevation/ShadowStyle.purs","start":[134,3]},"title":"Layered"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Elevation","ShadowStyle"],"Intensity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","RGB"],"RGBA"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Elevation","Shadow"],"LayeredShadow"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[135,12],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Elevation/ShadowStyle.purs","start":[135,3]},"title":"Colored"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Elevation","ShadowStyle"],"Intensity"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Elevation","Shadow"],"LayeredShadow"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[136,9],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Elevation/ShadowStyle.purs","start":[136,3]},"title":"Long"},{"comments":null,"info":{"declType":"instance","dependencies":[],"type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Data","Eq"],"Eq"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Elevation","ShadowStyle"],"ShadowStyle"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"s